The language_name filter returns the language name given its two-letter code: <br>

{# German #}
{{ 'de'|language_name }} <br>

By default, the filter uses the current locale. You can pass it explicitly: <br>

{# allemand #}
{{ 'de'|language_name('fr') }} <br>

{# fran√ßais canadien #}
{{ 'fr_CA'|language_name('fr_FR') }} <br>
